-- Reduce Exposure to China Property Stocks in Near Term, Credit Suisse Says
-- B y   S h i y i n   C h e n
-- 2010-09-29T23:45:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-29/reduce-exposure-to-china-property-stocks-in-near-term-credit-suisse-says.html
Investors should continue reducing
their exposure to Chinese property stocks in the near term
after the government yesterday announced further measures to
cool the industry, according to Credit Suisse Group AG.  The measures announced are “not yet reflected” in share
prices, with Hong Kong-listed developers likely to fall more
than those traded on the mainland, according to a report by
analysts led by Jinsong Du.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shiyin Chen in Singapore at 
